title: Duplicate Images - Data Cleaning
description: While exploring the data I found that there are 778 duplicate images. There are 3 types of data errors regarding duplicate images: 1) The same image with the corresponding Id appears multiple time. 2) The same image appears with a known whale Id and as "new_whale". 3) The same image appears with different Ids (ambiguous classified). The following code shows a data cleaning approach to fix the duplicate images issue.
